## SECTION=hosttools_platform

config HOST_OXNAS_TOOLS
	tristate
	default ALLYES
	help
	  OXNAS tools provides a collection of small host programs you
	  need for cross development target the Oxford Semiconductors
	  OXE8x0 SATA network controller (OXNAS).

	  If you want to generate especially payload blobs for the OXNAS
	  boot rom you will need the program mkoxnasblob from this tool
	  collection. If you want to setup disk images that can understand
	  by the OXNAS boot rom you will need the program setupoxnasmbr
	  from this tool collection.
